@mozilla/web-qa-sorcerers r?

This is the initial version of FxAPOM. 

As can be seen from the readme, it includes a method for creating a FxA, as well as a helper which can be used to sign in via FxA.  I am looking for feedback on this before making the initial commit to Mozilla/master. I will also be releasing this as a PyPI package when it has passed review.

Note that this code is already being run in production by marketplace-tests and marketplace-tests-gaia, both pointing at my repo.

